snippet.title: Jazz Hero Spotlight | Heart Electric
snippet.description:
"Jazz’s love of nature and all its creatures knows no boundaries, and she spends most of her time exploring the wooded outskirts of Silicon Hope.

During her initial sub world dives she found an incredibly powerful memory trace from a young human girl who’s bond with her pet knew no boundaries. Moved by the strength of this bond, Jazz felt it was her single most valuable trace and it’s now kept, and adored, as “Otto”, Jazz’s very own pet fly who she loves more than anything.

As a complete Gen3 and one of the youngest Synths in the valley, her modifications are varied and distinctly non-human. Her unique camouflage skin offers protection from the elements, but also allows her to get close to both wary animals and opponents in battle."
